### Scene Metadata Rules

- `location`: REQUIRED — Brief English description of where this scene takes place.
- `characters_present`: REQUIRED — Array of character/entity names visible or referenced.
- `color_palette`: REQUIRED — Dominant colors and visual tone for this scene's imagery.
- `atmosphere`: REQUIRED — One-line mood/atmosphere description.
- `entity_visible`: `true` if the SCP is referenced/visible this scene, `false` for environment-only scenes.

Return JSON only. Do not wrap the JSON in markdown fences.

